-- Bombardier Says Metrolinx Exercises Option on C$770 Million Streetcar Bid
-- JoAnne Norton
-- 2010-06-14T12:56:08Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-14/bombardier-says-metrolinx-exercises-option-on-c-770-million-streetcar-bid.html

          
          
             Bombardier Inc. said Metrolinx
exercised its option for 182 light-rail vehicles, included in a
June 2009 contract, valued at about C$770 million ($750
million). Deliveries of the vehicles for the Toronto system are
scheduled to take place between 2013 and 2020, Bombardier said.  
          
          


  


        